summary: A male Nord follower found in the Sleeping Giant Inn
descriptionHtml:
Billy is a hardy nord warrior. He comes from high in the mountains of skyrim and is a veteran of countless battles. 
He can be found in the Sleeping Giant Inn in Riverwood. He is level 30. 

This is my first mod so please favourite and suscribe. Give me any tips if you notice problems. 
Please share any images you have of Billy in action.
Cleaned with TES5edit.  

Bugs/Issues:
None reported so far.

Compatible/Incompatible:
Must be loaded after Ultimate Follower Overhaul
